
	***********************************  ASSIGNMENT 3 *****************************************************************************
	********************************* DEVICE DRIVER G547 **************************************************************************

1. Compile the source code and Make file using make all.

2. Insert the module using sudo insmod main.ko.

3. Insert the pendrive.

4. Remove the already existing driver using 
	1. sudo rmmod uas.

	2. sudo rmmod usb_storage.

5. To check the usb driver got added using sudo fdisk -l.

6. Create a directory in media sudo mkdir /media/rusb

7. Mount USB driver into media 
	sudo mount -t vfat /dev/myDriver1/media/rusb

   //device mount  operation  happen in the kernel log.

8. sudo -i (to go to root folder).

9. cd /media/rusb .

10. ls (Check the usb content).

11. echo anshu > text.txt (File gets created).
    
12. cat text.txt ( Read the contents of the file).

13. cd .. / ..

14. unmount /media/rusb 		/unmount

15. Logout of the kernel. 

16. Remove the pendrive

***************************************************END***************************************************************************************
